highlights.text: YUNGTARR has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “Satin” is the highest at #32.
“One Of My Life” by BLVCKHEART and K6Y has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 245 days straight.
“Montagem Supersonic” by KHAOS and Jmilton is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 15 spots at #83.
